name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lich Pathfinder- Wrath Of The Righteous Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Step into the dark and mystical world of Pathfinder with the awe-inspiring Lich theme for your browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Immerse yourself in the eerie allure of Lich Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous live wallpaper. This extension brings the sinister beauty of the Lich to life, featuring dark tones and magical energy perfect for fans of this iconic RPG.

Key Features:
🧙 Lich-Themed Visuals: Witness the haunting essence of the Lich in vivid detail every time you open a new tab.
🔍 Custom Search Functionality: Search seamlessly using your default search engine.
🕒 Clock and Date Display: Stay organized with a sleek time and date interface.
🌐 Site Shortcuts: Quickly access your favorite links from the homepage.
🎮 RPG-Inspired Design: A must-have for Pathfinder fans and RPG enthusiasts.
Transform your Chrome experience with the dark magic of Pathfinder and explore the righteous battle against evil!
